Set default values for run configuration inside the tuple clone method. Tuples do not appear to have constructors, but this seems to do the trick.
Introduce TableRef to hold a reference to a table imported or created in the script being edited.
Color gene list reference the same color as the gene list name in definitions.
partial commit before quick fix.
finish with TableRef work.
Set image name from statement id, so that the filename is fixed across executions. Correct calculation of multiplot width from width of included sub-plots.
Add ability to customize the style of a fit x by y plot. change xlabel, ylabel and title with style.
Convert fit x by y to use the scatterplot function in the car package (http://www.inside-r.org/packages/cran/car/docs/scatterplot)
Fix mtext generation.
Add the ability to define xmin xmax on scatterplots.
Add support for strings in expressions. This makes it possible to subset the allogenomics cohorts into validation and discovery and generate figures 1 and 2 automatically.
Write r^2 with an expression to format nicely.

Introduce ability to render a plot (or multi-plot) to PDF. Had to revert the use of scatterplot from car to graphics, because car does not play nicely with mfrow/mfcol and this is necessary to package multiple plots on one page.
partial commit
